Help To Upload Data of Your Nutrigarden To
poshanvatika.communitygis.net
Step 1: Register – Data uploaded by the user will be
accepted only when user is registered. To register please
expand the drop-down menu on the website
While registration please make sure you set up a password
with more than 8 characters and inclusive of alphanumeric
Step 2: Fill the Form: You can access the Pre-Defined
form through the drop-down button or by link provided
inside “My Poshanvatika” page
Step 3: Capture the Nutri-Garden: Here you need to
upload the Nutri-Garden Image with very short & basic
info
